{"tid":87170,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死2隻]滑雪場三日內兩死亡事故　10歲童墮崖亡","createTime":"2017-01-19T15:02:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-29T06:42:21.000Z","uid":32407,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6b684008d76c93e67302f82b4b21f6d47153c0e7","tid":87170,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T15:02:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170119/bkncn-20170119130521443-0119_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170119%2Fbkncn-20170119130521443-0119_05011_001.html&d=IFw9uHpJ9pOiX7uGL2cN3EsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=c7dea66a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170119/bkncn-20170119130521443-0119_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n北京冬季奧運會將於2022年舉行，作為主要賽事舉辦場地的河北張家口市崇禮縣，近日卻接連發生滑雪事故，遭市民質疑安全措施不足。當地傳媒指，三日內已有兩人不幸身亡，分別為一名北京大學女學生及一名年約10歲的男童；有知情人士透露，兩人均有一定滑雪經驗。<br />\n<br />\n據報，女死者為北大資訊科學技術學院研究生，本月16日與朋友到萬龍滑雪場滑雪時意外身亡。知情人士透露，女生是穿過旗門後未有減速，結果撞樹死亡；救援人員趕至時，只見女生倒在血泊，「所有人當時都不敢動。」<br />\n<br />\n另有滑雪愛好者昨日爆料稱，一個年約10歲的男童在太舞滑雪場道外被巡邏人員發現。當時男童已身受重傷，送院時不治身亡。而縣人民醫院工作人員證實，曾有男童因滑雪事故被送至該院急診科，但「小孩到醫院時已經不行了」。<br />\n<br />\n過唔到年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"412273534e726b9e8476aab1d0037ba466eea711","tid":87170,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T15:10:56.000Z","msg":"又係北京搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff04914f4006047d22934b9d62dc00ad9568314f","tid":87170,"uid":49316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T07:02:58.000Z","msg":"十年前支那雪場用鐵棍做場邊圍欄。有人起速埋去插死佐<br />\n<br />\n其實應該用膠棍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1261405b96f5a1d6b8db2c991dcfea0e66c6151c","tid":87170,"uid":25221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T06:34:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"53d951d6d23f3356c8f8b6fe7fe44e3cc4922683","tid":87170,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T06:39:17.000Z","msg":"十歲可以有咩滑雪經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d52423c09e4e9ee270fc9987bd311bd5862084be","tid":87170,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T06:42:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>十歲可以有咩滑雪經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n出事之前滑過兩步=經驗"}]}